These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, disaster, scientific, spy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, ambient, punk, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, australian, malaysian, british
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, train, skateboard, airplane
1. the australian is the fan of soul##1
2. the malaysian is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching spy movies##2
3. the australian is the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the japanese##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
8. the japanese is on the far right##1
9. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | spy   | superhero  | scientific  |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | soul    | hip-hop      | punk    |
| Nationality   | british | australian | malaysian | japanese |
| Transport     | airplane  | scooter       | train    | skateboard     |

