.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, hiking, rock-climbing, dancing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, romance, family, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: pony, hamster, goldfish, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, skiing, volleyball, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the snake is the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is between the owner of the goldfish and the person who's sport is climbing##2
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person watching time-travel movies and the owner of the snake##2
7. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
8. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
9. the person watching family movies is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | dancing | hiking    | rock-climbing  | photography    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie      | romance  | time-travel  | family |
| Pet           | snake      | goldfish       | hamster      | pony       |
| Sport         | skiing    | biathlon | volleyball | climbing |

