.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, zucchini, grapefruit, cranberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, filmmaking, reading, hiking
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, musician, doctor, freelancer
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, scooter, bike
1. the doctor is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the freelancer##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the musician is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
8. the person eating pineapple is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
9. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person eating grapefruit and the musician##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | zucchini | grapefruit     | pineapple   | cranberry     |
| Hobby       | filmmaking   | board-games   | reading | hiking |
| Job         | journalist   | doctor | freelancer       | musician    |
| Transport   | scooter    | quad-bike | trike  | bike    |

