 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is the owner of the cat##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 7. the person watching animation movies is the designer##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 9. the analyst is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
10. the architect is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the dressmaker##2

.:: Answer ::.
