 4. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 6. the person eating apple is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 7. the accountant is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 8. the project-manager is the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person eating apple is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person watching horror movies##2
10. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
