 8. the owner of the ferret is between the person eating peas and the person eating eggplant##2
 9. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person eating peas and the person eating eggplant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
